zzo-reveals-her-new-album-love-in-real-life-is-finished-3848039">她的新专辑《现实生活中的爱》是“完成的”</a> ，她将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><em>《周六夜现场》</em></a>上演出。这是在她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-music-video-for-lizzos-funky-indie-rock-comeback-single-love-in-real-life-3842164">以前在上个月发行了LP的唱片曲目为主打单曲</a>之后，此后一直放弃毫无歉意的歌曲“<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lizzos-unapologetic-new-single-still-bad-3846004">Still Bad</a> ”。专辑尚未收到发行日期。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-to-play-rock-n-roll-pioneer-sister-rosetta-tharpe-in-upcoming-biopic-3848888">Lizzo在即将上映的传记片中扮演Rock&#39;n&#39;Roll先驱姐妹Rosetta Tharpe的</a>邮报首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
