rena-tour-with-the-lottery-winners-buy-tickets-3549632">在去年的英国和欧洲竞技场巡回赛上支持“您如何让我想起我的摇滚乐手”</a> 。专辑中的其他嘉宾包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-turner">弗兰克·特纳（Frank Turner）</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">Shed Shed</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reverend-and-the-makers">Reverend＆The Makers。</a></p><p>彩票获奖者将于下个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lottery-winners-announce-keep-on-keeping-on-2025-uk-tour-tickets-3800813">继续前进英国的头条新闻巡回赛</a>。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/lottery-winners-tickets/artist/2169944?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=xOnTBHWu7xyKRF4SKGSfxVZQUks0aAVlGVH-Tg0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到剩余的门票</a>。此外，乐队将于今年在英国节日巡回演出，定于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-sting-stereophonics-announced-headliners-isle-of-wight-festival-2025-3796064">怀特岛节</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendal-calling-2024-line-up-the-prodigy-courteeners-fatboy-slim-kaiser-chiefs-and-more-announced-buy-tickets-3808588">肯德尔召唤</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bearded-theory-adds-paul-heaton-english-teacher-nadine-shah-the-lottery-winners-and-more-to-stacked-2025-line-up-3828411">胡须理论</a>等。</p><p>他们还将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-2025-uk-ireland-europe-tour-buy-tickets-3811519">今年夏天在爱丁堡，伦敦，曼彻斯特和巴斯在英国举行的大型体育场表演中为罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）开幕</a>。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Frobbie-williams-tickets%2Fartist%2F783976" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到门票。</p><p> NME上的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lottery-winners-on-course-for-second-uk-number-one-album-with-koko-3848785">第一张英国第二张专辑中的彩票获奖者</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现。</p> ;
